<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākēbdē nidhināgabhānugaṇitē caitrē sitāyāṁ
<lb n="2"/>tithau paṁcamyāṁ ravivāsarē naraharērdhupadvayē cāma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>raṁ paṭṭānāyaka sa<unclear>tsu</unclear>dhīḥ hari <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> dhīśasya <unclear>saṁ</unclear>vījitu<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>bhaktyādāt paḍirāyamāṁkuraniśaṁ śrīkīrtipuṇyapriya[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
<lb n="5"/>sakavaruṣaṁbulu 1289 gunēṁṭi caitra bahaḷa paṁcami
<lb n="6"/>bhānuvāramunāṁḍu paṭṭānāyaka māṁkāyapaḍirā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yaṁḍu tanaku niṣṭārtthasiddhigā śrīnarasiṁhanāthu<unclear>ni</unclear>
<lb n="8"/>śrībhaṁḍāramaṁdu padmanidhigaṁḍamāḍalu 5 peṭṭi [O*] 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ka kuṁca prasādamu nelapaḍi Appalu 3 Ēṁḍādi jītamu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lu cinnalu 4 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 7 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Iṁtavaṭṭunnu vṛttigā baḍasi nityamunnu
<lb n="11"/>Ubhayadhūpāla parvvāla tiruvīdhulannu cāmarapaṭṭanu
<lb n="12"/>narisakaruṇaṁ pōlāsāniki Ācaṁdrārkasthayigāṁ be
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmuvu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

